OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with some bright
OL,6,For sunny spells. Turning cloudier in
OL,7,Fthe afternoon as a band of rain and
OL,8,Fhill snow spreads eastwards to most
OL,9,Fparts, accompanied by strengthening
OL,10,Fwinds. Staying mostly dry towards
OL,11,FInverness and Nairn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with rain
OL,14,Fand hill snow continuing to spread
OL,15,Feastwards, heavy at times. Rain
OL,16,Fclearing east overnight, replaced by
OL,17,Fshowers and drier spells. Strongest
OL,18,Fwinds easing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
