OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FBlustery showers feeding in
OL,6,Ffrom the west throughout the day, with
OL,7,Fsome bright spells between showers.
OL,8,FSnow over hills at first but becoming
OL,9,Fincreasingly wintry to low levels
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FShowers
OL,13,Fand bright spells early Saturday, then
OL,14,Frain and strong winds spreading north
OL,15,Flater, risk of gales. Blustery showers
OL,16,Fwith gale risk easing Sunday. Mostly
OL,17,Fdry and windy on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
